<title>BELGIUM: EU Commission 97/98 economic forecast for Britain.</title>
<headline>EU Commission 97/98 economic forecast for Britain.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1997-04-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Following are the economic forecasts by the European Commission for Britain, released on Wednesday:</p>
<p>				     1997	 1998</p>
<p> GDP growth (pct)		2.8	   2.6</p>
<p> Investment			6.0	   7.0</p>
<p> GDP price deflator (pct)    2.3	   2.5</p>
<p> Unemployment (pct)	    6.8	   6.3</p>
<p> Public sector deficit	 2.9	   1.4</p>
<p>(pct of GDP)</p>
<p> Debt/GDP ratio		 54.7	  53.8</p>
</text>
